title: Guidance: Tri-service accommodation regulations (TSARs) (JSP 464)
text: 6 March 2017 Added updated Volume 1 Parts 1&2, Volume 2 Parts 1&2 and Volume 3 Part 1 2 February 2017 Updated: Service family accommodation (SFA) and substitute service family accommodation, UK and Overseas: directive 9 January 2017 Added updated JSP 464 Volume 1 Parts 1, Volume 2 Parts 1 and 2 and Volume 3 Part 1 14 November 2016 Replaced JSP 464 Volume 1 Parts 1 and 2 and Volume 2 Part 1 4 May 2016 Added updated JSP 464 Vol 1, Part 2 with amendments to telephone numbers. 26 April 2016 Added updated Vol2 Part 2 document. 1 March 2016 Added updated versions JSP 464 Volume 3 Parts 1 and 2. 22 February 2016 Added updated Vol 1 parts 1 and 2. Added updated Vol 2 parts 1 and 2. 26 January 2016 Added updated Vol1 parts 1 and 2; Vol 2 part 2 24 November 2015 Added updated versions of JSP Vol 3 Parts 1 and 2. 17 September 2015 Updated all documents to the latest versions. 8 May 2015 Added revised parts for 1 to 4. 3 December 2014 Added replacement versions of Part 1 and Part 3. 2 December 2014
